# Initial Go-to-Market Strategy

Although the long-term market opportunity spans multiple institutional sectors, BCSentinel will initially focus on a highly specialised customer segment.

The first commercial deployments will target organisations where early information provides the highest strategic value.

Priority customers include:

• Hedge Funds

• Venture Capital Firms

• Digital Asset Investment Firms

• Institutional Asset Managers

• Specialized Family Offices

This focused strategy enables rapid product refinement before expanding into additional institutional markets.

